import React from 'react'
import { BrowserRouter, Routes, Route } from 'react-router-dom'
import MainPage from './components/MainPage'


function App () {
    return (
        <MainPage />,
        
        <BrowserRouter>
          <Routes>
              <Route path='/' element={<MainPage />} />
          </Routes>
        </BrowserRouter>
    )
}

export default App
